Move over tycoons, the baddest coaster in the land is coming straight for the SEGA Dreamcast.
Coaster Works serves up much more than your typical roller coaster game.
Build your own death defying tracks, or trade them on-line with friends.
No matter how you play, hold on, because Coaster Works will be the most intense ride of your life.